{"tid":2304833,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"勵敬懲教所懲教人員初步確診 曾探病同一病房有病人確診","createTime":"2020-11-29T06:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T09:47:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"872f525090072e4c12531841771b3f3f902a7f7c","tid":2304833,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"勵敬懲教所一名更生事務組懲教人員初步確診新型冠狀病毒，目前正在東區醫院接受治療。懲教署指，有關職員最近一次上班是上星期二，同日接獲衞生防護中心通知她於上周休假期間前往外間醫院探病，同一病房有病人其後確診，被介定為密切接觸者，翌日被安排入住竹篙灣檢疫中心接受檢疫，昨晚獲通知初步確診。懲教署指，職員最近沒有外遊紀錄，於工作時有佩戴外科口罩，並與接觸人士保持適當社交距離，上班期間一直有探熱，體溫正常。 <br />\n<br />\n懲教署對相關地方進行徹底清潔消毒，並會安排懲教所內所有職員及在囚人士再次進行病毒測試；在囚人士及有密切接觸職員日前測試樣本全部均為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2368487&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR1lsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=2b54a303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368487</a>"},{"pid":"457e9012415fae6e6c73256846f95086f0bc5057","tid":2304833,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"黑懲中左招唔驚啦<br />\n都無得惹比屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4557a960d301486203435e63ee585be7d803df6","tid":2304833,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286bb30765f75a4e07ed03010ae631dc53cedd3c","tid":2304833,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 